    skos:definition "Sampling rate of the collection of perfomance indicators.<br/><br/><br/><br/>Supported values are : 1mn, 5mn, 15mn, 30mn, 1h, 24h, not applicable. <br/><br/>Note that litterals cannot start by a digit, so they are prefixed by a letter.<br/>"@en ;
