    skos:definition "Questions/Comments:<br/><br/>ClosedLoopRelationship<br/>- Don't normally use composition for relationship classes?<br/>- Multiplicity (2 / *)?<br/>- Need two relationships?<br/> - A requires B?<br/>- Difference with ClosedLoopRelationship?<br/>CONCLUSION: Delete This entity and ClosedLoopRelatiionshipSpecification entities - will be covered via the direct relationship between ClosedLoopSPec and ClosedLoop<br/><br/>ClosedLoopGroup<br/>- Composition? Group can have many CLSpecs<br/>- multiplicity: - 0..1 versus 0..*<br/> - Can a given CLSpec be in more than one group?<br/>- CreateDate attribute not required?<br/>- Make aggregation from ClosedLoopGroup<br/><br/>ClosedLoopType<br/>- Check Multiplicity. IG1220F has 0..* / 1..*). <br/>- Can a type have 0 relationships?<br/>- Modeling as not composition<br/><br/>ClosedLoopModel<br/>- Modeling as not composition<br/><br/><br/>ClosedLoopPartyRole<br/>- Composition?<br/><br/>ClosedLoopMeasure<br/>- Need definition (not in IG1220F 3.1 list)<br/>- Inherits from RootEntity?<br/>- Attribute descriptions?<br/><br/>ClosedLoopManagement<br/>- Multiplicty?<br/><br/>ClosedLoopBusinessRule<br/>- Definition?<br/>- Located in what ABE/Package<br/>- attribute description<br/><br/>ClosedLoopEndBy or ClsoedLoopExitBy<br/><br/>ClosedLoopPriority?<br/><br/>ClosedLoopLifecycle?<br/>- In the diagram with no associations<br/><br/>ClosedLoopState?<br/>- In the diagram with no associations<br/>"@en ;
    skos:inScheme thes:sid ;
    skos:notation "sid:EARoot_EA4_EA2_EA10_EA18_EA6037" ;
    skos:prefLabel "EARoot_EA4_EA2_EA10_EA18_EA6037"@en .

