    skos:definition "“Green & Gold” house is a multistory building in the central business district. This Service Provider has some human resources staff on the 5th floor.<br/>Janet Green is employed in the “Vitality Enablement” section of HR.<br/>On the 3rd floor there is a consulting group, which is a customer of this Service Provider. One of the Service Provider’s Products terminates there. If the place was deemed important enough, then a site & building entity could also be created.<br/>"@en ;
