<http://ots.local/thesaurus/sid/sid_EARoot_EA4_EA2_EA11_EA9_EA7229> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <http://ots.local/thesaurus/sid/sid_EARoot_EA4_EA2_EA11_EA9_EA7195> ;
    skos:definition "Why having added a relationship with PolicyRule as it is already specified (original contribution) through the fact that chosingRule attribute from DocSpecChar is of type PolicyRule)? Why should we need several rules?<br/>Same remarks for CharValueInformationType.<br/>"@en ;
