    skos:definition "<font color=\"#29313b\">A CompositeProductOfferingInstance represents the instantiation of a CompositeProductOfferingSpecification for a specific Customer. A CompositeProductOfferingInstance contains at least a ProducrOfferingInstance either Composite or Atomic.</font><br/>"@en ;
