<http://ots.local/thesaurus/sid/sid_EARoot_EA4_EA2_EA10_EA11_EA3_EA5425> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <http://ots.local/thesaurus/sid/sid_EARoot_EA4_EA2_EA10_EA11_EA5356> ;
    skos:definition "The Policy Framework Spec ABE contains entities that define the invariant characteristics and behavior of policy entities. This enables multiple instances to be derived from a single specification entity. In this derivation, each instance will use the invariant characteristics and behavior defined in its associated template.<br/><br/>This domain includes specifications for a PolicyRule, its components, and how multiple PolicyRules can be grouped together.<br/>"@en ;
